#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:53
msgid ""
"**FLAG_RELATIVE_PATHS** = **1** --- Save the resource with a path "
"relative to the scene which uses it."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:55
msgid "**FLAG_BUNDLE_RESOURCES** = **2** --- Bundles external resources."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:57
msgid ""
"**FLAG_CHANGE_PATH** = **4** --- Changes the :ref:`Resource.resource_path"
" <class_Resource_property_resource_path>` of the saved resource to match "
"its new location."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:59
msgid ""
"**FLAG_OMIT_EDITOR_PROPERTIES** = **8** --- Do not save editor-specific "
"metadata (identified by their ``__editor`` prefix)."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:61
msgid ""
"**FLAG_SAVE_BIG_ENDIAN** = **16** --- Save as big endian (see "
":ref:`File.endian_swap <class_File_property_endian_swap>`)."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:63
msgid ""
"**FLAG_COMPRESS** = **32** --- Compress the resource on save using "
":ref:`File.COMPRESSION_ZSTD <class_File_constant_COMPRESSION_ZSTD>`. Only"
" available for binary resource types."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_resourcesaver.rst:65
msgid ""
"**FLAG_REPLACE_SUBRESOURCE_PATHS** = **64** --- Take over the paths of "
"the saved subresources (see :ref:`Resource.take_over_path "
"<class_Resource_method_take_over_path>`)."
msgstr ""

